# Code owners for artifactory-gate.
#
# Review here is the single human approval gate in the issue-ops allowlist flow:
# the intake workflow opens a PR automatically, and a code owner reviewing and
# merging that PR is what actually approves a bypass. Auto-deploy then runs on
# merge to main.
#
# IMPORTANT: replace @your-org/your-team below with the correct GitHub team (or
# user) handle for this repo. A handle that does not resolve to a team with write
# access silently disables required-review enforcement.

# Allowlist source of truth (bypass approvals).
/allowlist.json            @your-org/your-team

# Runtime Worker source and the generated allowlist block within it.
/workers/                  @your-org/your-team

# Intake/deploy automation and the gate itself.
/.github/                  @your-org/your-team
/scripts/                  @your-org/your-team
